name: Airplane Games Jumbo Jet Parking 3D Airport Flight Plane Parking Simulator
name_original: Airplane Games Jumbo Jet Parking 3D Airport Flight Plane Parking Simulator
description:
Airplane Games Jumbo Jet Parking allows you to transport a plane full of valuable cargo from one point to the parking spot. Your responsibility is to drive and take the plane safely upto the marked zone. Do not damage your plane on the way or you will fail the level.
Lets start the parking mania now!

Game Features:-
*Explore different airplanes to drive and park
*Realistic Plane Physics
*Test your driving and parking skills now
*Upgrade your plane now!

How to Play:-
Tap your iPhone/iPad on right side to drive / brake.
Tap on left to control steering.
